%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D0%BE%D1%88%D0%BA%D0%B0\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nDecline the Russian noun картошка (kartoška) in all forms with usage examples and word stress. Картошка declension has never been easier!\n\n---\n\nTitle: картошка - Wiktionary, the free dictionary\nURL: https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D0%BE%D1%88%D0%BA%D0%B0\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\nFromкарто́ха(kartóxa) +‎-ка(-ka, diminutive ending), the former a dialectal variant ofкарто́фель(kartófelʹ, “potato”).[1] Recorded since the middle of the 19th century.\n...\n1. (colloquial) potato\n...\nDeclension of карто́шка (inan fem-form velar-stem accent-a reduc)\n...\nreform declension of карто́шка (inan fem-form velar-stem accent-a reduc)\n...\n- карто́шка в мунди́ре(kartóška v mundíre)\n...\n- карто́фель(kartófelʹ) (more formal),карто́фелина f (kartófelina)\n- карто́шина f (kartóšina)\n...\n| Regional synonyms of \"potato\" | Dari | کچالو |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| Iranian Persian | سیب‌زمینی |\n| Tajik | себзаминӣ, картошка |\n...\n### Alternative forms\n...\n- катӯшка(katüška) — dialectal, Khujand[1]\n...\nBorrowed from Russianкарто́шка (kartóška).\n...\n1. potato Synonym:себзаминӣ(sebzamini)\n\n---\n\nTitle: potato - Wikidata\nURL: https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q16587531\nPublished: N/A\nAuthor: N/A\nHighlights:\npotato - Wikidata\n\n \n\nstaple food\n...\nstaple food\n...\nDescription | Also known as |\n...\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n...\n| default for all\n...\n| English |\n...\nstaple food\n...\nKlexikon article ID\n...\n- arwikiبطاطا (ثمرة)\n- arzwikiبطاطس\n- aywiki Ch'uqi\n- barwiki Eadäpfe\n- bhwikiआलू\n- biwiki Kumala\n- bowikiཞོ་ཁོག\n- cebwiki Patatas\n- chrwikiᏄᎾ\n- csbwiki Bùlwa\n- diqwiki Kartole\n- elwikiΠατάτες\n- enwiki Potato (food)\n- etwiki Kartul\n- fiu_vrowiki Kardohkas\n- gdwiki Buntàta\n- htwiki Pòm tè\n- ikwiki Asiaġruaq\n- iowiki Terpomo\n- itwiki Patata (alimento)\n- kaawiki Kartoshka\n- krcwikiГардош\n- kshwikiÄäpel\n-